name: Best Meat In Town
description: I had halloween stuff planned. I forgot to cook this sucker. Just took it out of the freezer.   I'm going to have to burn the darn thing. Can you please tell any other virtual hobos how to get in on this boner_stevens (dQ5Dhv5zqNA) thing? ...I am giving you pennies. So that one day our pennies will be worth more...What do you think? Good for one day, maybe two more? Then we get some common household items and turn them into a cash cow. First single. Feels good that this will one day go to a good home.
